b'[![](../../cdshop/cdinfo.jpg)](../../cdshop/index.htm)  \n[Sacred Texts](../../index.htm)  [Hinduism](../index.htm)  [Index](index.htm)\n[Previous](sbe48331.htm)  [Next](sbe48333.htm)\n\n* * *\n\n15\\. Moreover there are seven.\n\nThe Sm _ri_ tis moreover declare that there are seven hells, called Raurava,\nand so on, to which evil-doers have to go.--But how do they, if moving about\nin those seven places, reach the palace of Yama?\n\n* * *\n\n[Next: 16. On account of his activity there also, there is no\ncontradiction](sbe48333.htm)\n\n'